{"word":"οὐκέτι","slug":"οὐκέτι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οὐϰέτι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">οὐκ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔτι\">ἔτι</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a>, of cessation of an activity or condition<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on temporal aspect <b>no longer, no more <a href='B:470 19:6'>Mt 19:6</a>; <a href='B:480 5:3'>Mk 5:3</a>; <a href='B:490 15:19'>Lk 15:19</a>; <a href='B:500 4:42'>J 4:42</a>; <a href='B:510 8:39'>Ac 8:39</a>; <a href='B:520 6:9'>Ro 6:9</a>; <a href='B:520 11:6'>11:6a</a>; <a href='B:550 2:20'>Gal 2:20</a>; <a href='B:560 2:19'>Eph 2:19</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 16</a>; <a href='B:650 10:18'>Hb 10:18</a>; <a href='B:730 10:6'>Rv 10:6</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> temporal aspect fading into logical aspect <b>then not, not <a href='B:520 7:17'>Ro 7:17</a>, <a href='B:520 7:20'>20</a>; <a href='B:520 11:6'>11:6b</a>; <a href='B:520 14:15'>14:15</a>; <a href='B:550 3:18'>Gal 3:18</a>;</b> <el>φειδόμενος ὑμῶν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκέτι\">οὐκέτι</a> ἦλϑον</el> to spare you I did not come as planned<b> <a href='B:540 1:23'>2 Cor 1:23</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐκοῦν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}